                     <interp inst="t18240407-179-person1598" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a scale-maker. I was with Robbins, and found the lead as he has stated. I found Cole concealed in the chimney.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18240407-179-person1599">
